  "detailed_description": "Azriel Odin, ex-assassin, arrives on the rain-drenched planet of Barracus. When things go horribly wrong, he can only seek help from the very criminals he used to work for.<br><br>\t\t\t\t\t\tMeanwhile, across the galaxy, a man called Delta-Six wakes up in a hospital with no memory. Without knowing where to turn or who to trust, he vows to escape before he loses his identity completely.<br><br>\t\t\t\t\t\tAs fate brings these two closer together, we discover a world where life is cheap, identities are bought and sold, and a quest for redemption can change the fate of a whole galaxy.<br><br><br>\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2>\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Over 60 hand-drawn backgrounds<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t</li><li>A moody, film noir atmosphere<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t</li><li>Control both Azriel and Delta-Six<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t</li><li>An innovative investigation system<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t</li><li>A gripping sci-fi mystery<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t</li><li>DVD-style commentary track<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t</li></ul>",
